[1 message from Lin Mo]

33
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,630
[The one who took Zhen Quan's belongings away is in Factory X.]

34
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,360
Beixing.

35
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,190
Mmm?

36
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,520
I asked Lin Mo

37
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,430
to track the phone signal

38
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,000
of the person who took your uncle's belongings away.

39
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,240
I just got some leads.

40
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:33,840
He is in Factory X.

41
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,910
Perhaps he

42
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,800
is the key to solving the mystery of my uncle's death.

43
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,910
Finish your food.

44
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,310
I'll go out now.

45
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:43,000
No.

46
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,560
I'll come with you this time.

47
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:45,310
No way.

48
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:46,190
