49
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:46,910
Gu Chen.

50
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:49,240
I can't just wait behind you all the time.

51
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,800
Beixing, I...

52
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,030
If you don't bring me with you,

53
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:55,310
he will help me locate you.

54
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,800
Gu Chen.

55
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,750
I just want the truth.

56
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,840
The truth of my father's death

57
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,030
and my uncle's death.

58
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:06,520
Every time we have a lead, it disappears quickly.

59
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:08,630
This could be

60
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:11,190
the closest we've ever been to the truth.

61
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,800
So I must come with you.

62
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:17,800
Okay. Promise me

63
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,910
you'll never leave my side.

64
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,240
I don't want anything bad to happen to you.

65
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:20,800
Understood?

66
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,680
Yes.

67
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,430
Okay. Let's go.

68
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:33,000
Gu Chen.

69
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:36,030
Do you think we'll find the truth this time?

70
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,190
We will as long as

71
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,310
we don't give up.

72
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,840
I trust you. Let's go.

73
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,560
We're here.

74
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:07,400
It looks like it was abandoned a long time ago.

75
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,360
It's creepy.

76
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,800
We must be careful.

77
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:11,750
God knows

78
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:13,630
what's inside.

79
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,470
Okay.

80
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:42,630
It seems like they were experimenting on gems.

81
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,480
Look at these gems.

82
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,950
They have different colors.

83
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,600
We got the right place then.

84
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:48,950
They must have been

85
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:50,600
studying the energy stones here,

86
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,630
including the Flutterheart Ring.

87
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,360
Did they notice we're here?

88
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,270
I'm not sure.

89
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:00,920
Stay vigilant.

90
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,430
Let's go.

91
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,720
So they are experimenting on gems.

92
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,950
Look at the machine.

93
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:26,000
It is testing the gem's energy.

94
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,510
If I'm not mistaken,

95
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,160
they are looking

96
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,160
for a powerful gem.

97
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,040
And the Flutterheart Ring is one of their targets.

98
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:39,310
Oh, no.

99
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,430
Our signal is jammed.

100
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,390
What do we do?

101
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:43,560
It's okay.

102
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,000
The message I had sent to Lin Mo

103
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,800
before we arrived contained our coordinates.

104
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:50,360
If I don't reply within an hour,

105
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:52,120
he'll find a way to locate us.

106
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,240
Let's look for more clues

107
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,510
and then leave.

108
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,310
Mo.

109
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,390
Surprise!

110
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,720
I'm here to hang out with you.

111
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:12,800
Hey!

112
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,800
Did you hear me?

113
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:19,510
Fine.

114
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:21,190
You're ignoring me, huh?

115
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:22,630
Hmph!

116
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,600
Ms. Su.

117
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,040
What do you want to do today?

118
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:48,830
I want

119
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:50,360
to play a game with you.

120
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,430
The loser has to agree

121
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:54,240
to whatever the winner demands.

122
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:57,360
Are you sure?

123
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,950
Very sure.

124
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:01,310
And I know what I want from you.

125
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,120
Okay.

126
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,950
What do we play?

127
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,920
Hmmm...

128
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,430
Let's...

129
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,950
Let's play sudoku.

130
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:08,750
Okay.

131
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,750
[Round 1]
Why is it not responding?

132
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,750
I'm done.

133
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,390
Let's play chess.

134
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,950
It's not fun.

135
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:21,160
Let's play rock, paper, scissors.

136
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,240
Sure.

137
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,360
Rock, paper, scissors.

138
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:28,830
Rock, paper, scissors.

139
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,120
Rock, paper, scissors.

140
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,920
Come on, Mo.

141
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,830
You always win.

142
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,510
Come. Last round.

143
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,160
Okay.

144
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,920
I will win this time.

145
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,920
Rock, paper,

146
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,510
scissors.

147
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,240
You won.

148
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:52,800
Yay, Mo!

149
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,510
I won!

150
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,190
All right.

151
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,870
What do you want to do?

152
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:58,190
I want to...

153
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,510
What are you trying to do?

154
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,390
I want to put makeup on you.

155
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,120
No! No!

156
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,310
But you promised just now.

157
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:08,800
No.

158
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,720
Let me do it.

159
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,750
Oh, no.

160
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:38,910
It's been an hour.

161
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,670
Huh?

162
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:40,510
What?

163
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,270
Gu Chen and Zhen Beixing

164
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,390
might be in danger.

165
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:43,200
What?

166
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,750
Where are they?

167
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:46,120
Let's go find them.

168
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,620
[System Hacked]

169
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:55,550
They are here.

170
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,000
Okay.

171
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,790
I'll drive.

172
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,320
All right.

173
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,030
The equipment here is quite advanced.

174
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,720
And this is a rare gem.

175
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,630
What are they studying?

176
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,390
It seems

177
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,910
like they are studying

178
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:27,240
gems with special power.

179
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:42,440
The result is very promising.

180
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,390
We have reached 80%.

181
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,270
It was

182
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,510
the last test except for the Flutterheart Ring.

183
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,480
When you look

184
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,510
at the latest result,

185
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:52,440
you'll be shocked.

186
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:53,440
Okay.

187
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,200
I'll wait for you.

188
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,910
You won't be disappointed.

189
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:58,030
Okay.

190
00:10:07,220 --> 00:10:09,140
[System Hacked]

191
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:21,030
So they are studying the Flutterheart Ring.

192
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:22,240
We must

193
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:24,000
get their study reports as soon as possible

194
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,720
to expose their true agenda.

195
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,550
It must be difficult to crack the computer's password.

196
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:41,030
We must be quick.

197
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:41,960
I'll try.

198
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,550
Give me some time.

199
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,720
Time waits for no one.

200
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,240
I know.

201
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,240
Just one more minute.

202
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,100
[Security Code]

203
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,390
We got it.

204
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:56,000
Their research is quite in-depth.

205
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,030
They must have made a lot of progress.

206
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,720
We must take the reports away

207
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,720
so that we can investigate and analyze it.

208
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:02,670
But now,

209
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:04,750
let's find a way out.

210
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,120
We must be careful.

211
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,910
Don't let them see us.

212
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:08,720
Let's go.

213
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,200
Who's there?

214
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,630
Come out now.

215
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,120
Someone has entered the room.

216
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,240
Find them.

217
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:23,870
Noted.

218
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,390
Quick. Over here.

219
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:33,550
There's no one here.

220
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,120
Oh.

221
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,120
I must have made a mistake.

222
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,510
There is no one here.

223
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,670
Search other areas.

224
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,120
Okay.

225
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:54,840
That was close.

226
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,550
They almost found us.

227
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,000
We can't take any more risks.

228
00:11:58,550 --> 00:12:01,750
We must hand this to the police now.

229
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,030
Let's get out of here.

230
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:04,200
Come.

231
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:08,550
Capture them.

232
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:20,760
♪The hazy streets rewind, bidding farewell to every heartbroken visitor♪

233
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:28,440
♪Parting flowers wither and fall, their lingering fragrance fades away♪

234
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:36,400
♪Your figure is swallowed by the crowd, as if you never stood by my side♪

235
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:45,960
♪The once moving vows vanish with the passing of time, who remembers them?♪

236
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:51,450
♪It's hard to define what I've truly possessed until now♪

237
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:56,440
♪Was it you or just memories? Snow melts, winter passes♪

238
00:12:57,120 --> 00:13:02,440
♪Everything is like our fleeting encounter, how can one let it go?♪

239
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:07,280
♪It's hard to define what I've truly possessed until now♪

240
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:13,140
♪Was it love or regret? Amid the river of time and sea of people♪

241
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:21,160
♪You and I embrace only for a moment before we part unwillingly♪
